<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> F.Wustenfeld: Die Chroniken der Stodt Mekka Leipzig ١٨٥٧ - ١٩٥٩, ١,٤٣٥,٥٠١ F., ii, ١٨٥ and index<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
